---
// Team - Founder card, organizational status, and contact info (GROW-05, GROW-06, GROW-07)
---

<section class="team section" id="team">
  <div class="container container--default">
    <div class="team__intro reveal">
      <div class="section-label">The Team</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Who's Building This</h2>
      <p class="section-body" style="margin-inline: auto;">
        Intelligent Economics is an open research project. The framework is built in public, the data is open, and the methodology is designed to be challenged and improved. We're assembling the founding cohort now — economists, engineers, policy thinkers, and community organizers who believe prosperity measurement should serve people, not just markets.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="team__card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
      <div class="team__info">
        <h3 class="team__name">Founding Team Forming</h3>
        <p class="team__bio">
          We're looking for economists to validate the model, engineers to build the dashboard, policy experts to design the pilot, and organizers to find the first city. If you have relevant expertise and want to help shape this from the ground up, we want to hear from you.
        </p>
        <a href="#volunteer" class="btn btn--primary" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: var(--space-4); font-size: var(--text-sm);">Join the Founding Team</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="team__status reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <span class="team__status-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      Organized as a nonprofit research organization. The MIND Index is a public good — open data, open methodology, open source.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .team__intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .team__intro .section-label {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .team__intro .section-label::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .team__intro .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .team__card {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: rgba(10, 10, 16, 0.55);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(1.2);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(1.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .team__avatar {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .team__avatar svg {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
  }

  .team__info {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .team__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .team__role {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .team__bio {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .team__contact {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-1);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 200ms ease;
  }

  .team__contact:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .team__status {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.15);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .team__status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-primary-glow);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: team-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes team-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .team__card {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .team__contact {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .team__status {
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
